fields.title: Picasso blue self portrait
fields.caption: I figured my first post on Kollektiv should of course be a self-portrait 💁‍♂️. Here I am at the age of 20 in my 🔵 blue 🔵 period.

fields.title: Dali - Geopoliticus
fields.caption: This is something I painted when I was in America in the '40s and symbolises the changing geopolitics of the time, but today it's simply giving me Monday feels 💀

fields.title: Gentileschi - Judith
fields.caption: I completed this painting not long after a very traumatic experience. Incredibly cathartic while I awaited real justice 🔥 🔥 🔥 Literally #slaying 💪

fields.title: Hepworth - Three Forms
fields.caption: I made this work not long after the birth of my triplets 💮💮💮

fields.title: Bourgeois - Maman
fields.caption: An ode to my own belle maman, who was also weaver 🕷️

fields.text: Looking good, Pablo! A very serious looking 20 year old.
